## 1. AUTHENTICATION

| ID | Scenario | Expected Outcome | Ref |
|---|---|---|---|
| A1 | Sign up with new email | Account created; profile row inserted; user lands on Home | — |
| A2 | Sign in with existing email + password | Session restored; auth bootstrap completes; MainTabView shown | `client_guardrails.me §7` |
| A3 | Sign in with wrong password | "Invalid email or password" shown; no navigation | — |
| A4 | App relaunch with valid session | User auto-authenticated; no sign-in screen shown | — |
