## 2. BOOKING — FREE GAMES

| ID | Scenario | Expected Outcome | Ref |
|---|---|---|---|
| B1 | Book a free game with spots available | Booking row inserted (`status=confirmed`, `fee_paid=false`, `payment_method=null`); CTA changes to "Booked" | `system_contracts.me §2` |
| B2 | Book a free game that is full | User placed on waitlist (`status=waitlisted`); waitlist position shown | `system_contracts.me §1` |
| B3 | Cancel a confirmed free booking | Booking `status=cancelled`; CTA resets to "Book Now"; no credit issued | `system_contracts.me §5` |
| B4 | Two users book the last spot simultaneously | One succeeds; one receives "game is full" and is placed on waitlist | `edge_cases.me §1` |
| B5 | Double-tap on "Book Now" button | Only one booking row inserted; second tap is ignored; UI shows "Booked" | `edge_cases.me §1` |
| B6 | Waitlist player auto-promoted (free game) | Player's status changes to `confirmed`; spot fills; next in waitlist re-queued if further spots open | `system_contracts.me §4` |

