## 3. BOOKING — PAID GAMES

| ID | Scenario | Expected Outcome | Ref |
|---|---|---|---|
| P1 | Book a paid game; complete Stripe payment | PaymentSheet shown; on `.completed`, booking inserted with `fee_paid=true`, `payment_method="stripe"`, `stripe_payment_intent_id`, `platform_fee_cents`, `club_payout_cents` | `system_contracts.me §2` |
| P2 | Book a paid game; cancel Stripe PaymentSheet | No booking row inserted; no credits decremented; CTA resets to "Book · $X.XX" | `system_contracts.me §2`, `edge_cases.me §1` |
| P3 | Book a paid game; Stripe payment fails | No booking row inserted; "Payment failed. Please try again." shown | `ux_parity.me §13` |
| P4 | Book a paid game fully covered by credits | PaymentSheet NOT shown; booking inserted with `credits_applied_cents=totalFee`; credit balance decremented | `system_contracts.me §3` |
| P5 | Book a paid game partially covered by credits | PaymentSheet shown for net amount; on `.completed`, booking inserted with both `credits_applied_cents` and `platform_fee_cents` set | `system_contracts.me §2` |
| P6 | Credit deduction fails (balance drops between read and write) | "Could not apply credits. Please try again." shown; booking not inserted | `edge_cases.me §3` |
| P7 | Network lost after Stripe `.completed`, before booking insert | Retry UI shown; booking can be retried with same PaymentIntent ID | `edge_cases.me §1` |

