## 4. WAITLIST — PAID GAMES

| ID | Scenario | Expected Outcome | Ref |
|---|---|---|---|
| W1 | Player joins waitlist on full paid game | `status=waitlisted`, `waitlist_position` set; no payment taken | `system_contracts.me §4` |
| W2 | Server promotes player to `pending_payment` | FCM push received; game detail shows "Complete Booking · $X.XX"; hold countdown starts | `system_contracts.me §4`, `ux_parity.me §6` |
| W3 | Player completes payment within hold window | Booking transitions to `confirmed`; credits deducted if applied | `system_contracts.me §4` |
| W4 | Hold expires before player pays | `pending_payment` reverted to `waitlisted` at position 1; UI shows "Spot hold expired" + Refresh | `system_contracts.me §4`, `ux_parity.me §3` |
| W5 | Two admins trigger promotion simultaneously | Only one promotion succeeds (RPC row lock); second returns FALSE; only one FCM push sent | `edge_cases.me §2`, `backend_authority.me §2` |
| W6 | Player cancels during hold window | Booking `status=cancelled`; no credit issued (never paid); next waitlisted player promoted | `edge_cases.me §2` |
| W7 | Player in `pending_payment` opens app after hold expires | UI shows "Spot hold expired" (not countdown); Refresh button visible | `ux_parity.me §3` |

