## 5. CANCELLATION AND CREDITS

| ID | Scenario | Expected Outcome | Ref |
|---|---|---|---|
| C1 | Cancel a paid booking > 6h before game | Credit issued for `platform_fee_cents + club_payout_cents + credits_applied_cents`; credit sheet shown with amount and new balance | `system_contracts.me §5`, `ux_parity.me §5` |
| C2 | Cancel a paid booking ≤ 6h before game | Booking cancelled; NO credit issued; pre-cancel warning was shown; no credit sheet shown | `system_contracts.me §5`, `ux_parity.me §5` |
| C3 | Cancel a free booking | Booking cancelled; no credit; no credit sheet | `system_contracts.me §5` |
| C4 | Cancel a credit-only booking > 6h before game | Credit issued for `credits_applied_cents` only | `system_contracts.me §5` |
| C5 | Cancellation credit issued twice (network retry) | Only one credit transaction inserted (`credit_transactions` unique constraint prevents duplicate) | `edge_cases.me §3` |
| C6 | Credit balance display after cancellation | `creditBalanceByClubId[clubId]` updated; club detail and checkout reflect new balance immediately | `system_contracts.me §3` |
| C7 | Pre-cancel warning shown when within 6h | Modal shows "No credit will be issued within 6 hours of game start." | `ux_parity.me §5` |
| C8 | Pre-cancel confirmation shown when outside 6h | Modal shows "You will receive a $X.XX credit for this booking." | `ux_parity.me §5` |

