## 12. LAYOUT AND UX PARITY TESTS

Run on minimum supported device (360dp width):

| ID | Scenario | Expected Outcome |
|---|---|---|
| L1 | Open GameDetailScreen with 11+ attendees | Avatar row capped at N; `+X` badge shown; no horizontal scroll | `client_guardrails.me §5` |
| L2 | Open GameDetailScreen on 360dp device | No horizontal scroll; all cards fill width | `client_guardrails.me §5` |
| L3 | Long game title (30+ chars) in game card | Title truncates with ellipsis; card does not overflow | `client_guardrails.me §5` |
| L4 | Booking CTA labels match per state | "Book Now", "Book · $X.XX", "Complete Booking · $X.XX", "Booked", "On Waitlist · #X", "Spot hold expired" | `ux_parity.me §3` |
| L5 | Payment badge visible to admin only | "Card", "Comp", "Unpaid" badges shown in attendee list for admin; hidden for regular players | `ux_parity.me §4` |
| L6 | Club owner tools menu order | View/Edit Games → Create Game → divider → Club Settings → divider → Join Requests → Manage Members | `ux_parity.me §9` |

