## 13. REGRESSION TARGETS

After any change to booking, payment, credit, or cancellation flows, re-run:

- B1, B5, P1, P2, P3 (core booking paths)
- C1, C2, C5 (cancellation and credit idempotency)
- CR7 (optimistic credit update)
- W4, W5 (hold expiry and promotion race)
- DI6, DI7, DI8 (data integrity)
- L1, L2 (layout constraints)
